title: HELP MISSING d3dx9_39.dll
body:
windows 8 64 bits
WHEN I PLAY it said i missing         "d3dx9_39.dll "

help PLZ!

THANK YOU!

replies.body: This could be a permission setting on your OS or something else that might be blocking the file from being accessed.  To be sure, go over the [permissions](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/204134104-Setting-up-your-Permissions) guide to make sure there aren't any blocks.  That said, it's important to make sure that you actually have the necessary produces and updated versions to get things running, so make sure that your Windows and DirectX are up to date!  I hope that helps!
